column2: Made chainers try to get w/in 7 of there enemy to keep them on defensive.
Made archons be much more aggressive
Made chainers attack from a little farther
Made archons transfer flux between themselves so we reach 3000 faster
Made units send a low energon message more often.
Fixed wout bugging issues / switched to using wouts to spawn towers.
Made archons only give wouts flux when they are attacking.
Merged Taylors FollowArchon code.  Made efficiency improvements.
Made us spawn more wouts.  Made archons ignore non-shooting enemies.
